item.title: CVE-2023-5748|2024-09-17T14:18:30.321Z -- synology -- synology%20ssl%20vpn%20client
item.description: Buffer copy without checking size of input ('Classic Buffer Overflow') vulnerability in cgi component in Synology SSL VPN Client before 1.4.7-0687 allows local users to conduct denial-of-service attacks via unspecified vectors.
